sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor Player
participant QuizConsole
participant QuizRepository
participant QuizService
participant QuizJson as quiz.json

== System Initialization ==
QuizConsole->>QuizRepository: loadQuestions()
alt quiz.json exists
  QuizRepository->>QuizJson: read questions array
  QuizJson-->>QuizRepository: question records
  QuizRepository-->>QuizConsole: vector<Question>
else file missing
  QuizRepository-->>QuizConsole: empty question set
end
QuizConsole->>QuizService: setQuestions(questions)
QuizService-->>QuizConsole: system ready
QuizConsole-->>Player: Display menu(Start Quiz, View Last Score, Exit)

== Start Quiz ==
Player->>QuizConsole: Select "Start Quiz"
QuizConsole->>QuizService: hasQuestions()
alt question set is empty
  QuizService-->>QuizConsole: false
  QuizConsole-->>Player: Display "No questions available"
else questions available
  QuizService-->>QuizConsole: true
  QuizConsole->>QuizService: getQuestions()
  QuizService-->>QuizConsole: questions
  loop for each question
    QuizConsole-->>Player: Show question text and options
    Player->>QuizConsole: Enter answer choice
    QuizConsole->>QuizService: validateAnswerChoice(choice, optionCount)
    alt invalid choice
      QuizService-->>QuizConsole: false
      QuizConsole-->>Player: Prompt again with validation error
      Player->>QuizConsole: Re-enter answer choice
      QuizConsole->>QuizService: validateAnswerChoice(choice, optionCount)
      QuizService-->>QuizConsole: true
    else valid choice
      QuizService-->>QuizConsole: true
    end
    QuizConsole->>QuizConsole: record answer index
  end

  == Submit Quiz ==
  QuizConsole->>QuizService: submitQuiz(answerIndices)
  QuizService->>QuizService: calculateScore(answerIndices)
  QuizService->>QuizService: buildResult(answerIndices, score)
  QuizService-->>QuizConsole: Result
  QuizConsole-->>Player: Display final score

  == Review Answers ==
  QuizConsole->>QuizService: getLastResult()
  QuizService-->>QuizConsole: Result
  QuizConsole->>QuizService: getQuestions()
  QuizService-->>QuizConsole: questions
  loop for each question
    QuizConsole-->>Player: Display user answer and correct answer
  end
end

== View Last Score ==
Player->>QuizConsole: Select "View Last Score"
QuizConsole->>QuizService: hasLastScore()
alt score exists
  QuizService-->>QuizConsole: true
  QuizConsole->>QuizService: getLastResult()
  QuizService-->>QuizConsole: Result
  QuizConsole-->>Player: Display last recorded score
else no submitted quiz yet
  QuizService-->>QuizConsole: false
  QuizConsole-->>Player: Display "No score recorded yet"
end

== Exit ==
Player->>QuizConsole: Select "Exit"
QuizConsole-->>Player: Terminate application
